t; &amp;amp; &lt;code&gt;Android&lt;/code&gt;：&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.shinnku.com/api/download/0/apk/%E5%86%B7%E7%8B%90/1500-2000/1536-%E6%AD%BB%E6%A3%BA-%E6%BF%92%E6%AD%BB%E8%BD%AE%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%BF%E4%BA%8E%E9%A6%86%E4%B8%AD%E8%90%8C%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%86%8E%E6%81%B6.apk&#34;&gt;点击下载&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;</description>
